verbose_text: The animals that received L-Ala-Gln demonstrated significantly reduced positive-IHC neurons of NF-kappaB levels on the internal pyramidal layer of the parietal region, detected through immunohistochemistry in the cortex of parietal region, after 30 and 60 minutes, respectively when compared to saline (0.9% NaCl) group (p = 0.001) (XREF_TABLE).
